Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:12.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Morning in Ponyville shimmers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Morning in Ponyville shines
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:19.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I know for absolute certain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:23.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That everything is certainly fine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:27.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's the Mayor en route to her office
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:31.29,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Morning, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:31.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's the sofa clerk selling some quills
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:35.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My Ponyville is so gentle and still
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:38.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Can things ever go wrong? \N I don't think that they will
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:45.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Morning in Ponyville shimmers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:48.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Morning in Ponyville shines
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:52.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I know for absolute certain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:54.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That everything is certainly…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash. That's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:00.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Terribly sorry, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:02.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I'm...I'm not good with the thundery ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:07.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Something tells me everything is not going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:50.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? What happened to your cutie mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:52.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Whatever do you mean, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:55.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm simply doing what I've done since the day it first appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Doesn't my sky look fabulous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:02.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Too last season?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Where is Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why isn't she handling this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:12.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what you had to wake me up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:14.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,I love sleeping in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's not about the weather, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity had Rainbow Dash's cutie mark
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:20.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and said this was Rainbow Dash's cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:23.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Something strange is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:27.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:30.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! Why is Rarity doing your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And what in Equestria is going on in…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:36.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,These animals don't listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,no not one little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:46.32,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,They run around out of control and throw their hissy fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's up to me to stop them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,'cause plainly you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's got to be my destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:56.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and it's what my cutie mark is telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:03.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I try to keep them laughing, put a smile upon their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:07.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But no matter what I try it seems a bit of a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.86,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I have to entertain them, it's there for all to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:14.67,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's got to be my destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:18.18,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,and it's what my cutie mark is telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:25.27,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I don't care much for pickin' fruit and plowing fields ain't judge-a-hoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:29.59,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,No matter what I try I cannot fix this busted water chute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:34.14,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I've got so many chores to do, it's no fun being me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:37.05,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But it has to be my destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.69,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,'cause it's what my cutie mark is telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:47.42,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Looky here at what I made, I think that it's a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:51.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I know it doesn't look like much, I'm under some distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:55.40,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Could y'all give a hand here and help me fix this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.44,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,My destiny is not pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.97,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but it's what my cutie mark is telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with weather patterns
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but the others have concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:12.77,Rarity,,0,0,0,,For I just gave them frost bite over top of their sun burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:17.97,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I have to keep on trying for everyone can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:20.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's got to be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.07,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's got to be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,My destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,My destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And it's what my cutie mark
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's what my cutie mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:30.40,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's what my cutie mark is telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is bad. This is very, very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Last night when you were taking one of your seven-hour bubble baths,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I got a special delivery from the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Twilight Sparkle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spell contained on the last page of this book{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is Star Swirl the Bearded's secret unfinished masterpiece.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:01.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was never able to get it right, and thus abandoned it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:05.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believe you  are the only pony who can understand and rewrite it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess Celestia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From one to another, another to one. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:14.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mark of one's destiny singled out alone, fulfilled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:20.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That doesn't make any sense. It doesn't even rhyme!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I cast the spell so I could find out what it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but nothing seemed to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But now I know something did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:31.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The spell has changed the Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:34.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That must be why their cutie marks are all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:37.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,So just cast a counter-spell to switch them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There is no counter-spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:42.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,Why don't you use that memory spell you used to fix everypony when Discord was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's not their memories Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,it's their true selves that have been altered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,Zecora's cure for the Cutie Pox?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:50.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That won't work either…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it won't be so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:56.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe our friends will grow to like their new lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No Spike. Their not who they are meant to be anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Their destinies are now changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:16.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have to find a way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:20.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,To make this all okay
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:24.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this small mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:27.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Could've caused so much heartache
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:31.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh why
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:35.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh why
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:39.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Losing promise
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:43.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:47.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Seeking answers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:54.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I fear I won't get through to you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh why
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:05.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh why
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:09.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike, what have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.59,Spike,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, Twilight, you'll figure out a way to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,These are your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're right, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And they mean more to me than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight? Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've got it! I know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:40.93,Spike,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:43.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to remind them of  who they are
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:46.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but I can show them what they mean to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They'll find the part of themselves that's been lost
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,so they can help the friends they care about so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh… hey, Twilight…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:02.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.06,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm moving back to Cloudsdale…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:08.83,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's wrong, but I can't seem to make anypony laugh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Before you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:16.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you might be willing to help Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She's really struggling with her animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:19.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:23.37,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't really know anything about animals…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But you do know something about Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.59,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I… know that she's a true friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:33.25,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,and I'll do anything I can to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:39.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:42.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm in here! Help! I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Twilight! Can't you do some sort of spell to get her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:50.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No. Fluttershy, you're the only one who can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash needs you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:57.69,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Um… hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:00.67,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Little… woodland creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.22,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know that you're all very upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:08.18,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,feel like giving Rainbow Dash a hard time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:12.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,but we'd all really appreciate it if you'd calm down and maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,rest for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.59,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh! Uh... look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:21.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Here's some nice, juicy leaves for you to munch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:25.07,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And some crunchy, munchy acorns too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:28.67,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, wouldn't you like to take a break and have a little snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.12,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Aww, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:36.17,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I guess you were all just cranky because you were hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:41.36,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are very welcome, little friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:46.58,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Goodness, I think I can understand them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:49.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I… I  feel strange, like…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:53.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,this is what I'm meant to do... like this is who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:55.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,My destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Wha... what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, look! Your cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It worked, it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:16.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so happy you're back to normal! Now we need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:20.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A true, true friend helps a friend in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:24.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A friend will be there to help them see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:28.03,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A true, true friend helps a friend in need
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:33.00,Somepony,,0,0,0,,to see the light that shines from a true, true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:35.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hello! Friend trapped inside, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity needs your help
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:42.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She's trying hard doing what she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:47.19,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Would you try, just give it a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:51.29,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You might find that you'll start to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:55.48,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A true, true friend helps a friend in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:59.51,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A friend will be there to help you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:03.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A true, true friend helps a friend in need
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:08.76,Somepony,,0,0,0,,to see the light that shines from a true, true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:11.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Uh, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's no time to explain, but we need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Applejack's trying to make dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Say no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Applejack needs your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:26.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She's trying hard doing what she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:30.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Would you try, just give it a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:33.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You might find that you'll start to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:38.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A true, true friend helps a friend in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:42.55,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A friend will be there to help them see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:46.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A true, true friend helps a friend in need
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:51.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,to see the light that shines from a true, true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:54.84,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what a terrible dream I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:57.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Or, maybe I'm still having it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity, Pinkie Pie is about to lose the apple farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We need Applejack's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Lose the apple farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.78,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well we can't let that happen, now can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:09.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie is in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:13.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We need to get there by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:17.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We can try to do what we can now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:21.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Or together we can be her guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:25.28,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A true, true friend helps a friend in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:29.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A friend will be there to help them see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:33.02,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A true, true friend helps a friend in need
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:39.40,Somepony,,0,0,0,,to see the light that shines from a true, true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.86,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yee-hah! Now that's more like it, what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:46.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The townspeople are furious, we need the old Pinkie Pie back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm on it, I know just the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:52.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The townspeople need you, they've been sad for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:56.54,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,They march around, faces frown and never seem to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:01.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And if you feel like helping, we'd appreciate a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:06.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,If you get up there and spread some cheer from here to Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:10.08,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Come on ponies, I wanna see you smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.28,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:15.51,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A true, true friend helps a friend in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:19.51,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A friend will be there to help them see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:23.06,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A true, true friend helps a friend in need
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.30,Somepony,,0,0,0,,to see the light (to see the light)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.30,Somepony,,0,0,0,,that shines (that shines)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:34.25,Somepony,,0,0,0,,from a true, true friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mark of one's destiny singled out alone, fulfilled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:42.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I understand now! I know how to fix the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:53.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For all of us together, together we're friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:58.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the marks of our destinies made one there's magic without end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:25.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:41.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Where am I? What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:49.16,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Twilight. I knew you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:53.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:56.64,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You did something today that's never been done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.37,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Something even a great unicorn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.88,Celestia,,0,0,0,,like Starswirl the Bearded was not able to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:05.12,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Because he did not understand friendship like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:09.81,Celestia,,0,0,0,,The lessons you learned here in Ponyville have taught you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:13.19,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You have proven that you ready, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:14.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:15.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ready for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:28.67,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You've come such a long-long way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:34.57,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And I've watched you from that very first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:37.61,Celestia,,0,0,0,,To see how you might grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:40.65,Celestia,,0,0,0,,To see what you might do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.86,Celestia,,0,0,0,,To see what you've been through
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:48.56,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And all the ways you've made me proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:58.47,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It's time now for a new change to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:04.61,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You've grown now and you new life has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:07.64,Celestia,,0,0,0,,To go where you will go,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:10.58,Celestia,,0,0,0,,To see what you will see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:12.61,Celestia,,0,0,0,,To find what you will be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:22.18,Celestia,,0,0,0,,For it's time for you to fullfill your destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Twilight..?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:52.82,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:02.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I've... I've never seen anything like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Twilight's got wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Awesome! A new flying buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Are you've became an Alicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know that was possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:15.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Alicorn party!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:18.80,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You look just like a Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.96,Celestia,,0,0,0,,That's because she is a Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.34,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Since you've come to Ponyville, you've displayed the charity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:44.55,Celestia,,0,0,0,,compassion, devotion, integrity, optimism
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:48.65,Celestia,,0,0,0,,and of course the leadership of a true Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:51.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But... Does this mean I won't be your student anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.94,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Not in the same way as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.21,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'll still be here to help and guide you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:59.31,Celestia,,0,0,0,,but we're all your students now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:03.24,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You are an inspiration to us all, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But… What would I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:12.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is there a book about being a princess I should read?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.71,Celestia,,0,0,0,,There will be time for all of that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:28.36,Celestia,,0,0,0,,We're gathered here today in celebration of a momentous occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:31.77,Celestia,,0,0,0,,My most faithful student, Twilight Sparkle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:35.69,Celestia,,0,0,0,,has done many extraordinary things since she's lived in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:40.03,Celestia,,0,0,0,,She even helped reunite me with my sister, Princess Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:45.20,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But today, Twilight Sparkle did something extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.94,Celestia,,0,0,0,,She created new magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.11,Celestia,,0,0,0,,proving without a doubt that she is ready to be crowned
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.82,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Equestria's newest princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:59.96,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Fillies and gentlecolts, may I present for the very first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:03.03,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:06.36,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The Princess Twilight cometh,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:09.75,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Behold, behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:13.02,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A Princess is before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:19.74,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Behold, behold, behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:23.05,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Behold, behold, behold, behold,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:26.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The Princess Twilight cometh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:29.73,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Behold, behold, behold, behold,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:33.50,Somepony,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,636.667)}The Princess is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.50,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The Princess is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.30,Somepony,,0,0,0,,HERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.56,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Say something, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A little while ago, my teacher and mentor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:50.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia sent me to live in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She sent me to study friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:56.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,which is something I didn't really care much about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But now, on a day like today,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:02.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can honestly say I wouldn't be standing here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:05.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,if it weren't for the friendships I've made with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:08.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Each one of you taught me something about friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:11.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and for that, I will always be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:16.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Today, I consider myself the luckiest pony in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:19.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thank you, friends. Thank you, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:26.88,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:28.88,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.44,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Of course not, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:36.18,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,it's liquid pride. Totally different thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:43.62,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Best coronation day ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:45.81,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We love you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:48.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I love you too, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:59.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The light in Equestria shimmers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:02.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Life in Equestria shines,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:06.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I know for absolute certain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:09.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:13.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes, everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:21.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes, everything is certainly fine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:25.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:30.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes! Everything's going to be just fine!
